hi

I'm sending you small Android app named OLinuXinoRomanNumbers to convert the decimal to Roman numbers for WPC#30.
Most of magic is done in toRoman method in class RomanConverter.

The code is uploaded at GitHub under GPLv2 licensee: 
https://github.com/leon-anavi/OLinuXinoRomanNumbers

The app is in Google Play. tested on Samsung Galaxy S2 and A10S-OLinuXino-MICRO+A13-LCD7TS :)

Regards
